  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_176_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……えっと……ここに……
おしょうゆをちょっと入れて……っと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uhm... So I put a little soy sauce here and...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_176_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お～、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;、エライだなぁ。
今日も一所懸命、頑張っているだか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, hey &lt;Mel&gt;! What a good girl you are!
I see you're trying hard as well today.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44316</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_176_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルトさん、ちょっと待ってくださいね、
美味しいお料理を開発中ですから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Albert! Please wait just a minute I'm still in the 
middle of making some tasty food.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_176_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>開発中ですと？　おおっ、ということは、
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;の創作料理が食べられるだか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In the middle, you say? Does that mean
I'll be able to eat your creative meals later?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_176_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なかなか美味しくできないんですけど、
がんばりますから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well it might not be the tastiest in the world,
but I'll do my best!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44672</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_176_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いんや～、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;は料理上手だで、心配ねーだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, I for sure know that your cooking is
the best in the world so I can rest assured!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_176_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そのうまい料理ができるまでに
誰が犠牲になってるか知ってんのか、てめぇ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You bastard... Did you even know who got 
sacrificed for that dish to become delicious!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
